titles: An elegie vpon the most deplorable death of Prince Henry, eldest sonne to the king of Bohemia who vpon the 9th of Ianuary last passing to Harlem, most unfortunately perished / [by] R. Abbey.
author: Abbey, R.
notes: Henry was the eldest son of Elizabeth of Bohemia, daughter of King James I.
Reproduction of original in: Society of Antiquaries.
keywords: Henry, --  Prince of Bohemia, d. 1629 --  Poetry.
